  - voice translation benchmark
  - comprehension fidelity
  - LLM-as-judge
abstract: >-
  Benchmark data for real-time voice translation quality. Includes a
  16-language-corridor comprehension benchmark (Turkish, Arabic, Indonesian,
  Vietnamese, Portuguese, Polish, Chinese, Malay source languages) and a
  latency + comprehension-fidelity benchmark (n=120, en to es/zh-CN/ja/de),
  comparing LiveLingo, Google, Azure, and Whisper + GPT-4o-mini on identical
  source audio, scored by three independent LLM judges.
